				<td colspan="2"><span>Yes, to go this way DO NOT go into the Hole via the door. Before you get to the courtyard newbie area in Panieel, there is a cliff ledge right by the tunnel to the newbie area.  That's the one you jump off of.  Hehe it only looks like suicide if you do things right (DA). <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />
Not that you can't get there going through the door, but it is MUCH harder and longer to fight your way through the entire zone, getting lost and maybe doing a painful CR.  This way it's a very quick in quick out mini-raid you can do every 6 hours for all your guild's bards and warriors!
<br />

<br />
Sinfonian</span></td>
