				<td colspan="2"><span>On EQ Atlas map, the jump point is about pos 775 pos 200.
<br />

<br />
Yes, DA is a group 18 second invunerability song that is level 60. 
<br />

<br />
If you decide to go through the door, it is basicaly to the bottom.  Even if you DON&quot;T have a 60 bard, it's best IMHO to DA your clerics and pallies to go down and clear any possible mobs there (I haven't seen any unless you aggro them through the walls), then suicide the rest of your raid and rez them all.  Adds a bit of time to the mix, but MUCH faster than going through the door.
<br />

<br />
Sinfonian</span></td>
