<br />

<br />
Alternate method to get your raid to Nortlav:  Tank, Healer, mage get DA'd and drop into pit.  Pick lock the door via the safer ent into the Hole and have the Mage then CotH the rest of the raid force down.
<br />

<br />
Suggestion to counteract the lifetap proc:  Similar as is done on VS.  Have a couple of chanters keep chain runing the main tank while the rest annihilate Nortlav.  If I remember correctly different runes stack and they absorb the lifetap without healing the mob.
